metadata.name: Seize and Share #1
metadata.description:
The genesis meme of Punk6529 has been seized, sharded and shared in 176 individual artworks. 

Seize and Share is both a homage to XCOPY Right Click Share and a project of collaboration for us in the open metaverse (om).

Will you be one of the 176 people to help reassemble 6529Seizing in the open metaverse (om)? 

Deadline is set for the great reveal on 31st December 2022.
